imdb.plot outline: "My Home Office" is a show that features the coolest stuff on the planet to turn your home office into a thriving business. The show also teaches you the etiquette of working from home and brings interviews with people that have successfully built multimillion dollar business from their homes.
imdb.title: My Home Office
